  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φοιβίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φοιβίου\">Φοιβίου</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φοιβίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φοιβίου\">ΦΟΙΒΙΟΥ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000869_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Reproduction of the drawing in Avolio 1827: 292\" src=\"ISic000869_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000869.jpg\"><img title=\"Reproduction of the drawing in Avolio 1827: 292\" src=\"ISic000869-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of IG (after Gaetani)</span>  </span>; </li><li><span><span>Avolio, MARPO inv: ΦΟΙΒΟΥ</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Not so far identified. The equivalence of MARPO inv. 2 with IG XIV.52 seems highly likely, but is not certain.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Avolio 1827 292 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002791\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002791</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">52</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Sgarlata 1993 128 no.12 </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
